.python-version

# pipenv
#   According to pypa/pipenv#598, it is recommended to include Pipfile.lock in version control.
#   However, in case of collaboration, if used in a vitualenv, it may be excluded.
#Strictly keep Pipfile.lock if you want reproducible builds.

# poetry
#   According to poetry markup, it is recommended to include poetry.lock in version control.
#   poetry.lock

